      "message": "Patch Set 1: Fails\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 5.8/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/fced7ef2-64e2-11e2-bfb2-52540035b04c).  Ran 12 tests.  1 tests failed: recovery-small.",
