        "inactive": true
      },
      "date": "2013-01-23 04:09:00.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nrecovery-small test_54 failed. With this patch introduced, client can't tell if the server has lost committed stuff after reboot anymore. (by checking last_committed before reconnect and after). see https://bugzilla.lustre.org/show_bug.cgi?id=9646.\r\n\r\nLet me think it over to see if there are any other better ways. (without protocol changes)",
