      "message": "Patch Set 2: Looks good to me, but someone else must approve\n\nbasically I agree but would think about better solution in master. I dislike this way because it is just not right to bump transaction for opens that don't need it at all, so this is pure client problem but we are 'simulating' server behavior just to make client behave properly.\nI'll put ideas in 2613 if any",
