      "date": "2013-05-31 20:27:09.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 3: I would prefer that you didn't submit this\n\n(2 inline comments)\n\nThis should really be submitted and landed to master before it is landed on b2_1.  This problem is longstanding, so there is no immediate rush to get it into 2.1 before ensuring it doesn't break anything.\n\nAlso, there should be some test case added for this, similar to sanity.sh test_76, but that is just running open/close of the same file in a loop (after a sync+sleep to ensure no in-flight RPCs will change last_committed during the test) and then some way to check if the RPC replay list is growing or not.",
