        "subject": "LU-2613 recovery: set fixed transno for rdonly open/close",
        "message": "LU-2613 recovery: set fixed transno for rdonly open/close\n\nAlways set the last_committed as the transno of rdonly open\nand close requests, so the retained open requests on client\ncan be freed promptly even when there isn't any update to\nthe filesystem.\n\nSigned-off-by: Niu Yawei <yawei.niu@intel.com>\nChange-Id: I93b9a5b9e87d323cd8916a8dc4f1a8a8ad4e373a\n"
